Class MockModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • MockModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Model
    public class MockModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements Model
    This class implements Model, but it is not a real class used for operations. This class is mainly used to log the operations results, data received from controller, which are used for testing actual model and controller.
